      config = {
         'threshold': 0.3,
         'min_scene_length': 2.0,
         'max_scenes': 500
      }




Performance Settings

























.. code-block:: python

      config = {
         'batch_size': 32,
         'use_gpu': True,
         'num_workers': 4
      }

