Usage Examples


--------------




--------------




--------------




--------------




--------------






Basic Detection

























.. code-block:: python

      detector = SceneDetector()
      scenes = detector.detect_scenes("video.mp4")




Advanced Options

























.. code-block:: python

      scenes = detector.detect_scenes(
         video,
         threshold=0.3,
         min_scene_length=2.0,
         max_scenes=500
      )

